*Nestalo* je mnogo vremena od kada smo se videli. (It has been a long time since we last saw each other.)

Sve što je bilo je *nestalo*. (Everything that was is gone.)

Niko ne zna gde je *nestalo* mnogo novca. (Nobody knows where a lot of money has gone.)

Uvek se osećam tužno kada mi *nestane* nečeg dragog. (I always feel sad when something dear to me disappears.)

*Nestalo* je mnogo ljudi sa ovog mesta. (Many people have left this place.)